      "text": "Acess to some essential resources is not uniform – influenced bt gender, parental status, age and type of contract\nMen report greater accessibility to most listed resources, except access to outdoor space\n\nNegative effect of motherhood on internet speed\nNot of fatherhood \nMaternity as an importante factor hampering women´s access to all resources",
